{
  "chapter": 4,
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_da_hu",
      "speaker_name": "沙大户",
      "listener": "char_yang_wu",
      "text": "你知不知道我在吃饭的时候，是从来不见外客的？",
      "tone": "质问",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_wu",
      "speaker_name": "杨五",
      "listener": "char_sha_da_hu",
      "text": "我知道。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_da_hu",
      "speaker_name": "沙大户",
      "listener": "char_yang_wu",
      "text": "那你为什么还不叫外面那个人滚蛋？",
      "tone": "命令",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_wu",
      "speaker_name": "杨五",
      "listener": "char_sha_da_hu",
      "text": "我本来不但想要他滚蛋，还想拎住他的脖子把他扔出去。",
      "tone": "解释",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_wu",
      "speaker_name": "杨五",
      "listener": "char_sha_da_hu",
      "text": "他没有把我扔出去，我已经很高兴了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_da_hu",
      "speaker_name": "沙大户",
      "listener": "char_yang_wu",
      "text": "我本来一直都以为你是一个很有种的人，怎么忽然会变得那么孬了？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_wu",
      "speaker_name": "杨五",
      "listener": "char_sha_da_hu",
      "text": "我一点都不孬。我只不过不想去惹那个人而已。",
      "tone": "辩解",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "孙先生",
      "listener": "char_yang_wu",
      "text": "那位仁兄究竟是何许人也？",
      "tone": "询问",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_wu",
      "speaker_name": "杨五",
      "listener": "char_sun_xian_sheng",
      "text": "他其实也不是什么了不起，只不过是个长了四条眉毛的陆小凤。",
      "tone": "故作冷淡",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "text": "你知不知道我是一个什么样的人？",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "text": "我是个骗吃骗喝的专家，就凭我的名字就可以吃遍天下。",
      "tone": "自嘲",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "老实和尚",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "这一次你说的实在是老实话。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_da_hu",
      "speaker_name": "沙大户",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "陆兄，你看这地方，像不像个菜市场？",
      "tone": "抱歉",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_sha_da_hu",
      "text": "真有点像。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_da_hu",
      "speaker_name": "沙大户",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "其实这个地方本来是蛮清静的，我们家也并不是这么没有规矩的人家，可是大家一听说那个能够用两根手指捏住刀锋，而且还有四条眉毛的陆小凤来了，谁都想看看这个陆小凤是个什么样的人。我挡也挡不住，赶也赶不走。",
      "tone": "解释",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这种事本来就是没法子的，谁叫我是这么有名的人？一个名人总是会常常碰到这种事的。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_sha_da_hu",
      "text": "我的穷、我的懒，都是很有名的，我相信你一定也知道。",
      "tone": "试探",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_da_hu",
      "speaker_name": "沙大户",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我听说过。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_sha_da_hu",
      "text": "那么你为什么不问我，像我这么样一个人怎么会像一只骡子一样，笨笨的赶了几千里路，连滚带爬的跑到这里来？",
      "tone": "引导",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_da_hu",
      "speaker_name": "沙大户",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "这地方实在越来越穷了，到这里来的人确实越来越少。像陆小凤这样的大人物居然会来，我们实在连作梦都想不到。幸好我不作梦的时候还可以想得到。",
      "tone": "感慨",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_sha_da_hu",
      "text": "你真的知道？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_da_hu",
      "speaker_name": "沙大户",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "真的。",
      "tone": "肯定",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_sha_da_hu",
      "text": "你知道些什么呢？",
      "tone": "追问",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_da_hu",
      "speaker_name": "沙大户",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "知道你是为了一个朋友来的，你那位朋友很不幸的死在这个地方。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_sha_da_hu",
      "text": "你知道的事好像还真不少。",
      "tone": "试探",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_da_hu",
      "speaker_name": "沙大户",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "这个地方虽然穷，我可不穷。像我这么样一个有钱人，总是有很多人会偷偷的跑来告诉我很多事的。有钱的人就好像有名的人一样，不管做什么事都要比别人方便一点。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_sha_da_hu",
      "text": "看起来你这个人实在真的是很有一点学问。",
      "tone": "恭维",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_da_hu",
      "speaker_name": "沙大户",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我的学问恐怕还不止一点而已。",
      "tone": "自得",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_sha_da_hu",
      "text": "除此以外，你还知道什么？",
      "tone": "追问",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_sha_da_hu",
      "text": "你是不是还知道我来找你是为了一把刀？",
      "tone": "试探",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_da_hu",
      "speaker_name": "沙大户",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "这种事我怎么可能不知道。这个小镇上怎么可能还有我不知道的事？",
      "tone": "自信",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_sha_da_hu",
      "text": "那么你一定也知道那两个人是谁了？",
      "tone": "追问",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_da_hu",
      "speaker_name": "沙大户",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "两个人？两个什么样的人？",
      "tone": "疑惑",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_sha_da_hu",
      "text": "你不知道我问的是哪两个人？",
      "tone": "反问",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_da_hu",
      "speaker_name": "沙大户",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我怎么会知道。这地方虽然小，人却不少，我怎么知道你问的是谁？",
      "tone": "不悦",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_sha_da_hu",
      "text": "原来这地方毕竟还是有些事是你不知道的。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_da_hu",
      "speaker_name": "沙大户",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你到底要找两个什么样的人？",
      "tone": "忍气",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_sha_da_hu",
      "text": "是一男一女。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_da_hu",
      "speaker_name": "沙大户",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你要找的是一男一女？好极了，实在好极了。这个世界上正好有一半是男人，一半是女人，你要找的正好就是一男一女，你说巧不巧？",
      "tone": "气极反笑",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_da_hu",
      "speaker_name": "沙大户",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "原来我上了你的当了。",
      "tone": "恍然",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_sha_da_hu",
      "text": "你上了我什么当？",
      "tone": "装傻",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_da_hu",
      "speaker_name": "沙大户",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你是故意在气我，我居然就真的生了气。我简直好像是个傻瓜。",
      "tone": "自嘲",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_da_hu",
      "speaker_name": "沙大户",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我看得出你也跟我一样，也是个争强好胜的人。我一向最喜欢这种人。",
      "tone": "欣赏",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_sha_da_hu",
      "text": "只可惜你长了胡子。你大概也知道陆先生一向只喜欢美女。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_da_hu",
      "speaker_name": "沙大户",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你要找的那一男一女，有什么特别跟别人不同的地方？",
      "tone": "询问",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_sha_da_hu",
      "text": "那个男的很会用刀。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_da_hu",
      "speaker_name": "沙大户",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我家的厨子也很会用刀，他用刀片起肉来，片得比纸还薄。你要找的是不是我的厨子？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_sha_da_hu",
      "text": "你的厨子会不会杀人？",
      "tone": "反问",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_da_hu",
      "speaker_name": "沙大户",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我只知道他会切肉。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_sha_da_hu",
      "text": "切什么肉？",
      "tone": "追问",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_da_hu",
      "speaker_name": "沙大户",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "猪肉牛肉羊肉狗肉骡肉马肉鸡肉鱼肉鹤肉鹅肉兔子肉獐子肉，什么肉他都切，甚至连老虎肉他都切过。只有一样肉他不切。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_sha_da_hu",
      "text": "人肉？",
      "tone": "接话",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_da_hu",
      "speaker_name": "沙大户",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你又说对了。人肉是酸的，比马肉还酸，我绝不会让我的厨子去切人肉。",
      "tone": "笑着",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_sha_da_hu",
      "text": "没有吃过人肉的人，怎么会知道人肉是酸的？真奇怪。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_da_hu",
      "speaker_name": "沙大户",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "男的会用刀，女的呢？",
      "tone": "询问",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_sha_da_hu",
      "text": "女的那一个就更奇怪了。她满头白发苍苍，像是个六七十岁的老太婆，可是她的一双腿，却像是个十六七岁的大姑娘。",
      "tone": "描述",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_da_hu",
      "speaker_name": "沙大户",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你有没有看到她的脸？",
      "tone": "询问",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_sha_da_hu",
      "text": "没有。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_da_hu",
      "speaker_name": "沙大户",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你为什么不看她的脸？",
      "tone": "追问",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_sha_da_hu",
      "text": "因为我是个男人。一个男人在看到那么样一双腿的时候，谁还有空去看她的脸？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_da_hu",
      "speaker_name": "沙大户",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "现在我才明白你的麻烦在哪里了。这个女人你根本就找不到，除非你能把这地方每个女人的裙子都脱下来瞧一瞧。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_sha_da_hu",
      "text": "老实告诉你，我正想这么做。",
      "tone": "正经",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_da_hu",
      "speaker_name": "沙大户",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "这种事谁不想做？如果你真的去做了，千万要告诉我，好让我也跟着你去瞧瞧。",
      "tone": "压低声音",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_jin_qi_liang",
      "text": "金老七，别人都能走，你不能走。",
      "tone": "大声",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_qi_liang",
      "speaker_name": "金老七",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "陆大侠，你在叫谁？",
      "tone": "装傻",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_jin_qi_liang",
      "text": "我不是大侠，就好像你也不是秀才一样。我在叫的当然就是江湖中惟一能'夜走千家，日盗百户'的金七两。",
      "tone": "揭穿",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_qi_liang",
      "speaker_name": "金老七",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我不认得这个人。",
      "tone": "否认",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_jin_qi_liang",
      "text": "你不认得我认得。你就是金七两，金七两就是你。",
      "tone": "肯定",
      "chapter": 4
    }
  ],
